name: Silent Notary
public_notice: Silent Notary has recently migrated from their old contract to a new one. For more information, please visit this post.

description.en: SilentNotary is a multiplatform decentralized service for confirmation of event existence. SilentNotary converts an event into legally significant evidence, excluding the possibility of falsification.
